      "before": "<p>A giant creates a fissure along the ground, either in a 15 × 2 line within 1 or a 10 × 3 line within 2, and that opens up to a depth of 6 squares. Each giant in the area can shift into the nearest unoccupied space outside the fissure. Each non-giant in the area makes an <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Agility test</span></strong></span>.</p><table><tbody><tr><td data-colwidth=\"98\"><p>11 or less</p></td><td><p>[[/damage 10]] damage; the target falls into the fissure, and is prone and can’t stand (EoT)</p></td></tr><tr><td data-colwidth=\"98\"><p>12–16</p></td><td><p>[[/damage 10]] damage; the target is prone and hanging onto the edge of the fissure</p></td></tr><tr><td data-colwidth=\"98\"><p>17+</p></td><td><p>The target can shift into the nearest unoccupied space outside the fissure.</p></td></tr></tbody></table>",
